task.summary: Default task
Got paperclip attachment delete working.
Added user authentication
Added walls, and wall browsing. Made images belong to walls. Added revisions.
Got the new CSS transform browser working in Firefox
Fleshed out the interface more with Bootstrap.
added missing /public files to git
Image now scales to window width if window is narrower than the image width.
Upon save, image will scale to window.
Body padding-top wasn't compensating for the fixed navbar.
Added re-do function
Drawing now clears the redo history.
Refactored the click state arrays into a single array with a datatype.
Added zoom, refactored some code.
Added Google OAuth2.0
Allowed user to move the photo during scaling.
Cleaned up Sign-in interface
Fixed javascript transformation bug.
Broke up the drawing menus into top and bottom
Unified zooming and navigation for image.
Fixed some strangeness happening with the mouse events. Changed the button bindings so that they bind with hammer js instead of jQuery.
Added ability to upload backgrounds from URLs
Added notification dialogs
Added QR codes
